	Moved mutt_perror (portable routine) from curs_lib to lib
	Added sendlib
	Can an autoconf guru fix the Makefile.am to not harcode RETSIGTYPE and SHARE

	* libmutt/sigblock.c:
	sigblock needs to own the Sigset-t object as its the one that may be linked
	alone

	* libmutt/globals.h, libmutt/globals.c:
	Ok this hopefully nails the global variable problem

	* libmutt/Makefile.am, libmutt/sigblock.c, libmutt/signal.c:
	Add more bits
	Split signal.c into two files as it contains both library and gui related
	pieces

	* libmutt/globals.h, libmutt/globals.c: Missed a few

