Thu Jul 16 16:36:57 1998  alan

	* src/Makefile.am:
	Link with the (as yet unfinished) libmutt not c-client

	* src/sendmsg-window.c, src/balsa-message.c, src/balsa-index.c:
	Fix old from->user references up. Also swat a couple of potential buffer
	overruns.

	Please use snprintf people

	* libbalsa/mailbox.c:
	Missing argument on check_mailbox. Close doesnt work the libbalsa way
	in libmutt. I think the change is right

	* libbalsa/mailbackend.h:
	Added libmutt/ to the includes otherwise the wrong mailbox.h is included
	libbalse now almost compiles

	* libmutt/globals.h, libmutt/init.c, libmutt/pager.c, libmutt/curs_main.c:
	libmutt has a string called "Status" in its globals. X windows defines
	Status to int. This is bad.

	libmutt now has a string called StatusString, this is good.

