	* src/save-restore.c, src/balsa-app.c, Attic/dotgnomeslashbalsa:
	made save-restore verify the type of mailbox instead of relying on the config
	file specified.  This shouldn't break backwards compat, since Type=0 for all
	local mailboxes, but imap/pop3/nntp remaned the same.

