	* src/main-window.c, src/Attic/index.h, src/Attic/index.c, src/balsa-index.h, src/balsa-index.c:
	Delete works.

	*NOTE* BE CAREFUL:
	It does *not* undelete (yet).  So if you mark a message read, you had better
	not exit through a normal means.. (so kill -9 it or something:)  or just be
	careful.

	It will (should) purge all messages marked delete upon exit or change in
	mailbox.  I'll put a better way to do this after i've done undelete.

	-pav

