	* /debian/home/gnomecvs/gnome-common/macros/gnome.m4, /debian/home/gnomecvs/gnome-common/macros/gnome-x-checks.m4, /debian/home/gnomecvs/gnome-common/macros/aclocal-include.m4, /debian/home/gnomecvs/gnome-common/macros/ChangeLog, /debian/home/gnomecvs/gnome-common/macros/Makefile.am:
